                    <h3>How Donation Works ?</h3>
                    <p id="basketball">Donating blood only takes around 10 minutes, but you should allow at least an
                        hour for the whole process (which includes a personal interview, recovery time and free
                        refreshments).
                        You can donate whole blood every 12 weeks, but you can donate plasma every 2 weeks.</p>
